About Event

​Join us for the January edition of the San Francisco AI Engineers Tech Talk, a gathering focused exclusively on AI engineering. Whether you’re a seasoned machine learning engineer or a fullstack dev curious about how to work with LLMs, this is your space to dive deep into real-world projects, technical challenges, and creative solutions.

What to Expect:
We invite AI engineers to share something they’ve built, the challenges they faced, and how they solved them. It’s all substance,
